!! Sub-brain delegation for monorepos and large projects
Detailed: Scatter autonomous .pinky/ sub-brains across subdirectories. Each sub-brain owns its subtree's files, rules, and notes. Root files.brain links to sub-brains as folder entries and never lists files inside delegated subtrees. On every request, iterate discovered sub-brains as categories — load relevant ones alongside root brain.
